===What is this?=== An application that help you download AKB48 girls' photos from their Google+ accounts AUTOMATICALLY. It will keep checking for new photos of your selected members periodically (when timer goes to 0).
===How to use=== 1.Select language to load Google+ member list and set download folder. 2.Select team or individual member to add to the Album list to download. 3.Add selected members to Album list. 4.Download all or download selected album list. 5.Wait for initial download to be completed. 6.Enjoy photos!
===Tips=== a.Keep the program open to let it auto check and download when timer becomes 0. b.You can open the program and click download all by yourself. You will get only new photos after the initial download is completed.
===Note=== This program generates "url.txt" and "downloadedURL.txt" automatically. Please keep these 2 files in the same directory as the program so that it works correctly.
===Known Issues=== 1.Duplicate photos are saved when resume downloading after suspension. 2.Cannot download more than 100 photos of each member. (Google+ page limitation)
===Development Information=== Developed using VB.NET language on Microsoft Visual Studio 2012. Developed by Chuy for all AKB48 fans. Facebook page: http://facebook.com/ChuyFansub
===Version History=== v0.0.0.1 Initial Release for testing purpose v1.0 All download processes are done in background. Fixed some bugs. Added picture player. Updated some layouts. V1.0.1 Fixed bug where Google+ team and member name list do not load correctly in PC with Internet Explorer 8. (Only in English G+) V1.0.2 Updated to support new Google+ webpage as of 2013/5/16 V1.0.3 Rearranged internal code. (2013/5/30) V1.0.4 Added staffs list. (2013/6/5) V1.0.5 Rearranged internal code. (2013/7/30) V1.0.6 Extract some variable to setting files (2014/1/2)
